Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.62,0:00:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,戌时已到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,犬夜叉马上要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.10,0:00:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,为了找齐四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.77,0:00:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,为了用这把铁碎牙打败奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.24,0:00:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,与七人帮终于进入决战阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,其中最后一位\N威力最大的亡魂  蛮骨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.27,0:00:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他的大镰刀蛮龙\N跟犬夜叉那把铁碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就要展开激烈比划
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,弥勒法师  珊瑚七宝跟云母
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,穿梭于时空\N发生在战国时代与现代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.05,0:00:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:25.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:32.15,OP,,0,0,0,,分散在蓝蓝天空上的 七颗星星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:36.86,OP,,0,0,0,,每一颗星星 都刻着我的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.17,0:00:40.77,OP,,0,0,0,,就算梦想被粉碎 我也要寻找爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.07,0:00:44.80,OP,,0,0,0,,我无处可逃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:48.87,OP,,0,0,0,,紧紧抓着我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:57.30,OP,,0,0,0,,那些骗人的光阴 我再也不会输给它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:02.67,OP,,0,0,0,,睁大眼睛 看清楚这瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.67,0:01:06.85,OP,,0,0,0,,它仍然紧紧围绕着我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:10.85,OP,,0,0,0,,让人啜泣的 现实生活中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.85,0:01:14.85,OP,,0,0,0,,最重要的…到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:18.72,OP,,0,0,0,,繁忙的这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:22.95,OP,,0,0,0,,永恒的碎片 忽隐又忽现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:26.87,OP,,0,0,0,,去触摸 去捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:33.80,OP,,0,0,0,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:39.03,OP,,0,0,0,,为了得到最后的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:46.27,OP,,0,0,0,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:01.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个是不是七人帮的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到瘦狼比笨狗来得更快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在那挣扎了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.79,0:02:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开  瘦皮狼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.33,0:02:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于找到你们了吧  七人帮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:03:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第111话\N火星撞地球 蛮龙对风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少来烦我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你就是犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到力气这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是\N七人帮的最后一个对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我是老大  蛮骨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会在那集众纠事\N欺负一只瘦皮狼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这只臭笨狗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我那么好欺负的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才你脚上那些四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差点就被抢走了  知不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会那么容易让人抢走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么这么慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都到齐了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干了那么多伤天害理的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.73,0:03:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我就把你们\N一起送回坟墓去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:03:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:04:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要帮凶骨跟雾骨\N两兄弟讨个公道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子拿大镰刀的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该就是他们的老大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过他的长相最年轻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心一点  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙\N脖子上有三块四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.93,0:04:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是雾骨跟凶骨的那份
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还真以为有三头六臂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这么回事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们身上的四魂之玉碎片\N一定是奈落给的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然会让你们几个杀人魔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重返人间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这的确很像奈落的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落要我们\N借着四魂之玉碎片的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你们几个全都给消灭掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.53,0:04:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上劈死你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有意思  尽管试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扭打起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不分轩轾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有闲情逸致在那看戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要东张西望的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:27.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是多担心自己吧  臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要紧吧  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总算做对了一件事\N没让戈薇受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭笨狗  别用那种\N高高在上的口气跟我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  真的很谢谢你  钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  快找个地方躲起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙\N想要我脚上的四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.98,0:05:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个叫炼骨的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从我身上\N偷走了四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还带在身上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个小姑娘她看得见\N我身上的四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次隐瞒了这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一让蛮骨大师兄发现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看他恐怕不会放过我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银骨  快杀了那个小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.19,0:06:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还不快跑  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就杀了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那么容易吗  这混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真以为可以打中我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离那座大炮远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得把碎片抢回来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被那个家伙\N抢走的四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧  弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.48,0:06:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别想能够过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡骨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天让老子陪你玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老子这辈子\N最恨的就是大夫跟和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己不也是大夫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真要命  怎么又是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.17,0:07:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一开始\N就挑到想要的对手了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道只留下这样的货色给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我这种货色  还真抱歉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪女人过招\N我还真的没什么兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:34.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少作梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不过是个半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只比人类难缠一点而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不明白\N为什么奈落一直没有干掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙  只有这么点本事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道奈落在哪里的话\N就赶快给我说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:07:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懒得回答你这些问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你那么想知道\N奈落在什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就问问我这把蛮龙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大一座山耶  邪见爷爷\N好不舒服啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:25.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我非得\N大老远跑到这种地方不可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  邪见爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.14,0:08:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道这座白灵山\N真的是圣地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.75,0:08:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我们妖怪来说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座山有一股干净到我们\N无法靠近的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小玲  你是个人类
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定感觉不出有任何异样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.55,0:08:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么感觉有人在拉我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再到前面看看吧  邪见爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本没在听嘛  这丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完了  这下完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天亡我也  天亡我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.95,0:09:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种地方\N应该不能容许奈落的妖气存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷\N他为什么偏偏要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是神圣的结界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路追踪奈落的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫琥珀的小鬼来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今气味就像消失了\N一点蛛丝马迹都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢哦  杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想早点离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.23,0:10:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底跑去哪里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爷会不会来救我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  是琥珀哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来  小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能一个人到处乱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.15,0:10:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别害我被杀生丸少爷骂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差一点就被结界给消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.53,0:10:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀哥哥  琥珀哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  终于又见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:10:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小玲  你怎么会到这来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.06,0:11:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次莫名其妙就跟你分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直好担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不是你该来的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别出声
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在慢慢的走回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁他们还没有发现你之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:23.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一被发现\N你会被他们给吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀哥哥  你不走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙不会攻击我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧  臭和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.34,0:11:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没那么容易就会死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别东张西望行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让地狱的烈火烧死你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会怕你这点小把戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.97,0:12:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的毒虫出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是最猛胜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道在叫我们撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.48,0:12:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦不烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我收拾完\N这几个家伙再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来想再多陪你们过几招的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就先留着你那条狗命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这话应该我说才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招  风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在才跑太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛮骨大师兄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道我的厉害了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然敢打伤我的蛮龙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银骨  你做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚多亏你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉\N今天就陪你玩到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙别想走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少在那悠闲地喝酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中计了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯独这个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.95,0:13:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要尽快把她杀了\N以免横生枝节
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼骨  这次你休想逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也未免太夸张了一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子是希望\N我们尽快赶回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些人  休想逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.73,0:14:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈…奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你原谅我  杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还来不及阻止小玲  她就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说小玲\N跑进结界了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:15:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万别这么做  杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一踏进圣地\N马上就会被消灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别罗唆了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看后面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  是小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀也在里面是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可要老老实实的回答少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何事情\N都别想瞒过我们的少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道杀生丸少爷\N真的要杀了琥珀哥哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事…事情是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是琥珀帮助小玲逃出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洞窟里面有好多好多妖怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.84,0:15:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么  有妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀哥哥一直保护小玲\N不被妖怪吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…所以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣地里怎么会有妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:54.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是奈落在故布疑阵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些笨蛋\N总算找到这来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  这个奈落恐怕是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.10,0:16:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用说一定是傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是想多争取一点时间\N好让七人帮跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪  怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.11,0:16:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个真的是傀儡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一定是奈落\N故意放出来的傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.72,0:16:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  跟以前那些傀儡\N似乎有些不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之是假的  没什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何人也别想过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然变得这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.31,0:16:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.27,0:16:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.14,0:16:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种纸老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁也别想过去…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙  你想抢功是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少废话  臭笨狗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.33,0:17:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续跟着你这个慢吞吞的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.07,0:17:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七人帮早就逃到老远了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这帮坏蛋\N应该还在这附近才对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我不会让你们跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子  你给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘发现了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个傀儡真的好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.75,0:17:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像太干净了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的傀儡居然会太干净
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟白灵山的感觉很像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白灵山
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?这味道怎么会这么香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个傀儡有水跟花的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水跟花的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:17:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过奈落的傀儡\N为什么会发出这种香味来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:09.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些坏蛋\N到底躲到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是结界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于看见了  蛮骨大师兄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.57,0:18:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白灵山就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这股空气真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比上次来的时候\N更让人不舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.74,0:18:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这边一点都感觉不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想应该是\N圣地的结界太强了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.25,0:18:37.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信这么一来\N犬夜叉跟钢牙那两个小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都没有办法追过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我们都觉得不舒服\N好歹我们还是人类呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来不需要劳师动众\N跑到山脚下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛮骨大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你啊  琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:19:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个惨白的小鬼是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是神无
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认得他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错不了的\N雾骨就是他干掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.85,0:19:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是犬夜叉的哥哥叫杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是犬夜叉的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也是我们要杀的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道就为了跟我们说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大老远把我们找回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才差点就干掉犬夜叉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再跟他纠缠下去\N你会被他杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.81,0:19:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在胡说什么  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.54,0:19:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就凭蛮骨那把大镰刀\N是打不过犬夜叉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.05,0:19:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是指\N我这把蛮龙挂了彩的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点小伤不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.06,0:19:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须变得更厉害一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼骨\N我看你还是乖乖交出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我全都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.34,0:20:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是指什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.04,0:20:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说我全都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.78,0:20:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把上次从那个\N叫戈薇的女孩身上偷来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉碎片给藏了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说\N你脖子上的四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.52,0:20:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我划开取出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先别发火  大师兄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本就想要交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算你聪明嘛  炼骨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几个兄弟里面\N果然你的脑筋最灵光了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望不要有下一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.21,0:20:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好  那么睡骨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有蛇骨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个\N马上帮我干掉杀生丸那小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.32,0:20:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不服气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是一向最喜欢男人的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只喜欢犬夜叉一个\N到底要人家说几次嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.96,0:21:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不过是你一厢情愿罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了这条心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.29,0:21:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉由我来解决
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经查出\N犬夜叉所在的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真不愧是个奸细呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.91,0:21:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不是奸细
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.92,0:21:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个半妖混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗干净脑袋等着瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.93,0:21:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到水边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道要搜河流跟沼泽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.17,0:21:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来没有闻过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.10,0:21:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种水味跟花香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.00,0:21:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确\N从来没有闻过这样的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.17,0:21:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是七人帮这件事怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我们继续追查奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.18,0:21:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七人帮迟早会现身的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落那混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓非把你找出来不可
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:37.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:13.20,ED,,0,0,0,,偷偷亲你一下 装作若无其事的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:18.27,ED,,0,0,0,,我这样调皮 是不是像个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.55,0:22:24.70,ED,,0,0,0,,早已习惯 被你说是娇嗔无理
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.70,0:22:34.42,ED,,0,0,0,,不过「喜欢你」这三个字却始终说不出口 My Sweet Emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.40,0:22:45.35,ED,,0,0,0,,对着镜子 多看一次 看看自己的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.12,0:22:58.65,ED,,0,0,0,,如果想飞奔出去追求刺激就得挺起胸膛向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:09.55,ED,,0,0,0,,大胆放手去做 直到满意为止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:18.60,ED,,0,0,0,,偷偷亲你一下 装作若无其事的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.60,0:23:23.77,ED,,0,0,0,,我这样调皮 是不是像个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.07,0:23:30.35,ED,,0,0,0,,早已习惯 被你说是娇嗔无理
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.35,0:23:39.82,ED,,0,0,0,,不过「喜欢你」这三个字却始终说不出口 My Sweet Emotion
